    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery across the rev range thanks to its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. This example has been properly maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's primary structural concerns. Suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the iconic handling characteristics and lateral grip are preserved. A mechanically sound specimen ready for spirited driving.",
