      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S that perfectly balances performance and utility. The exterior paint retains a brilliant, deep shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with light highway use. The 19-inch wheels are wrapped in premium Michelin tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership: the black leather upholstery is supple with no tears or heavy creasing, and the dash is free of any sun damage or cracks. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the panoramic sunroof and the updated infotainment system, operates as intended. Under the hood, the twin-turbo V6 runs smoothly, benefiting from a documented service history that includes a recent oil change and brake fluid flush. The PDK transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts without hesitation. This vehicle has been garage-kept, non-smoker owned, and comes with two keys and all original manuals. It is a reliable, high-performance daily driver that needs nothing but a new enthusiast behind the wheel.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
